Interface CompositeQuerySpace

  • All Superinterfaces:
    QuerySpace
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ExpandingCompositeQuerySpace
    public interface CompositeQuerySpace
extends QuerySpace
    Models a QuerySpace for a composition (component/embeddable).

    It's QuerySpace.getDisposition() result will be QuerySpace.Disposition.COMPOSITE
